WEBVTT

00:09:27.117 --> 00:09:30.546
Predictions link
the sensations in your body

00:09:30.570 --> 00:09:32.380
that give you these simple feelings

00:09:32.404 --> 00:09:34.459
with what's going on
around you in the world

00:09:34.483 --> 00:09:35.832
so that you know what to do.

00:09:35.856 --> 00:09:37.333
And sometimes,

00:09:37.357 --> 00:09:42.395
those constructions are emotions.

00:09:42.419 --> 00:09:47.174
So for example, if you were
to walk into a bakery,

00:09:47.198 --> 00:09:51.007
your brain might predict
that you will encounter

00:09:51.031 --> 00:09:55.110
the delicious aroma of freshly baked
chocolate chip cookies.

00:09:55.531 --> 00:09:57.266
I know my brain would predict

00:09:57.290 --> 00:09:59.897
the delicious aroma of freshly baked
chocolate cookies.

00:09:59.921 --> 00:10:02.912
And our brains might cause
our stomachs to churn a little bit,